<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Āyuḥ prājyamanaṁtasaṁpadamanaṁtānaṁdamiṁduprabhāṁ
<lb n="2"/>kīrttiṁ śāśvatasaṁtatiṁ bhuvi śubhākāraṁ ca sārasvataṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nṛharē
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rmṛgēṁdra<unclear>śikharāvāsē</unclear> śriyā saṁyutasya śrīpādasarōjasaktasumatē<unclear>ḥ</unclear> śrībhī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>manāryyaprabhōḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śākābdē girināgabhānugaṇitē māsē tathā cāśvinē kṛṣṇē
<lb n="5"/>ca pratipaddinē budhayutē śrīsiṁhaśailēśituḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> sō<unclear>ya</unclear>ṁ svarnnasahasradhāraruciraṁ 
<lb n="6"/>pātraṁ sitābhrānvitaṁ tāṁbū<unclear>la</unclear>ṁ ca nivēdituṁ svavihitakṣīrārppaṇānaṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>taraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1287 gunēṁṭi Āśvayuja bahaḷa prati
<lb n="8" break="no"/>padayu budhavāramunāṁḍu Oḍḍavādi bhīmanapegaḍa tanaku niṣṭārttha
<lb n="9" break="no"/>siddhigā śrīnarasiṁhanāthuniki tirumajjanāvasarānakuṁ beṭṭina pahiṁḍi saha
<lb n="10" break="no"/>sradhāra Okaṁḍu māpaṭi dhūpāvasaramaṁdu tana dattamaina pālāragiṁcina ve
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nakunu Oka karppuraviḍiyamu Āragiṁpanu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrībhaṁḍāramaṁdu padmanidhigaṁḍa
<lb n="12" break="no"/>māḍalu 60 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> peṭṭi nityamunnu 1 viḍiyamu Āṟu pōṁkalu pādikettu paccaka
<lb n="13" break="no"/>rppuramu Īṁtavaṭunnu māpaṭi dhūpāvasaramaṁdu tana dattamaina
<lb n="14"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/>giṁcina venakanu [A]ḍeṁḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="16"/>rakṣa nitya Oka kalaśa peṭṭenu śrībhaṁḍārāna reṁḍu māḍalu ve
<lb n="17" break="no"/><unclear>ṭenu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

